{"tid":1536821,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港人 真係要團結 唔好散","createTime":"2019-09-03T17:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T17:32:25.000Z","uid":3775,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d54d4bf0994aa80d5a778dfb2b8d1e1c2a732997","tid":1536821,"uid":3775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:26:11.000Z","msg":"夜夜有抗爭者走上街頭<br />\n晚晚有市民企出黎<br />\n到到今晚 唔少市民見到受害者癱瘓都只能圍住班畜牲，只可以唔比佢地繼續隨意加害<br />\n大家都知警權有幾大 郁手就要坐監 大家心內面有幾多怒有幾多哀 我諗係香港人都非常清楚<br />\n我係黃 係和理非 係懦夫 但我要呼籲大家<br />\n<br />\n一榮皆榮、一損皆損 <br />\n<br />\n和理非唔好怕左白色恐佈而唔再上街 罷唔到工都唔好唔用金錢資助 <br />\n行動不方便都唔好放網上留言 <br />\n因為聚沙可成塔<br />\n<br />\n記得我地無多個十年 只有現在 <br />\n<br />\n屌老你全家 死畜牲 無畜牲！<br />\n<br />\n準備做condom啦 智障無腦 <br />\n<br />\n你有人工都係香港人搵比你咋 你估你好叻？"},{"pid":"e07241a6a5cda62002477167584ac18a257882d2","tid":1536821,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:26:29.000Z","msg":"我每個post 都會咒一次：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警死全家</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">(集中討論) <br />\n908 九月八日 2:00pm <br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館<br />\n《香港人權及民主法案》集會請願 ! ! <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">扯國旗!</span> <span style=\"color: blue;\">唱國歌 !</span></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536086\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536086</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/kCGOYms.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCGOYms.jpg&h=ced74507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/JGPEpwY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJGPEpwY.jpg&h=115c89d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽歌隨意門(附歌詞):</span></span><br />\n<b